---
title: Sweet Chilli Chicken Burgers with Kumara Fries & Green Salad
description: As the sweet chilli sauce starts to caramelise on your chicken, you know there’s some magic at work. Full of fresh tomato, cucumber and lemon, there’s never a dull moment in this weeknight winner. What’s the best bit, you ask? We can’t decide!
